[head=1]Assertations[/head][/color]
[color=Gray]This section can be filled out by a legal representative or consultant for the witness, by a representative of the court, or by the witness themselves[/color]

Mark in each box if the associated statement is true. 
\[  ] This section is being filled by a representative of the witness.
\[  ] This section is being filled by a representative of the court.
\[  ] This section is being filled by the witness themselves.
\[  ] This affidavit was written while the witness was in a safe location
\[  ] The boxes in the affidavit were written in by the witness, and only the witness.
\[  ] Before signing this document, this document was not in the custody of an unathorized holder
\[  ] Mark this box if the Full Length Account was skipped due to time contraints.

[color=DarkSlateBlue]‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾[/color]

For the [bold]WITNESS:[/bold]
By signing this document, I certify that all sections of the filled boxed sections are correct and truthful. I am aware that by signing this document, all statement I made within this document are made under oath, and that to intentionally falsify information in this document is Perjury, a felony that, if charged, will result in imprisonment. Furthermore, if I also filled ou the Assertations portion of this document, I agree that all the information in that section is correct and truthful, under oath, and under threat of Purgery.

For the [bold]REPRESENTATIVE:[/bold] (if applicable)
By signing this document, I certify that I did NOT write, erase, or in any way modify the boxed sections of the Witness Affidavit. By signing this document, I certify that all sections of the Assertationts are correct and truthful, under oath, and under threat of Purjery.

